---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---
<Layout title="MealMap — Support" description="MealMap support and help.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
    <a href="/" class="text-white/30 hover:text-white text-sm transition mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-1">
      ← Back to Home
    </a>
    
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-2">Support — MealMap</h1>
    <p class="text-white/30 mb-10">We're here to help!</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">For any questions, issues, or feedback about MealMap, please email us at:</p>
    <a href="mailto:justinbundrick@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-red-500/20 border border-red-500/30 rounded-xl text-red-400 hover:text-red-300 font-medium transition">
      📧 justinbundrick@gmail.com
    </a>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Common Questions</h2>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">How do I restore my purchases?</h3>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Go to Settings → Restore Purchases. This will restore any active subscriptions linked to your Apple ID.</p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">How do I cancel my subscription?</h3>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Subscriptions are managed through Apple. Go to iPhone Settings → tap your name → Subscriptions → MealMap → Cancel. You'll retain access until the end of your current billing period.</p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">Is my data private?</h3>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Yes. Your meals, recipes, and plans are stored locally on your device (and in iCloud if enabled). AI conversations are processed in transit and not stored on our servers. See our <a href="/mealmap/privacy" class="text-red-400 hover:text-red-300 underline">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.</p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">What's included in the free tier?</h3>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Free users get up to 20 saved meals, the weekly calendar, Meal Roulette, Themed Nights, manual grocery lists, and URL recipe import. Premium unlocks Chef AI, Snap to Meal, Auto Plan, unlimited meals, smart grocery lists, and 52-week history.</p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white/90 mt-6 mb-3">The AI isn't responding / gives an error</h3>
    <p class="text-white/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">AI features require an internet connection. Check your Wi-Fi/cellular, then try again. If the issue persists, email us with a screenshot and we'll investigate.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
